pilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.overviewBody2":"You guide what your agent should know, how it should work, and how it should respond. Each step builds on the last, making your agent more powerful over time. You'll also be able to see how your agent is performing against your goals and how it improves with every change.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.overviewSubtitle":"Customise your agent for the work you want it to do","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.overviewTitle":"Agent Tuning","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.startTuningButton":"Start tuning","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.stepBadge1":"STEP 1 OF 3","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.stepBadge2":"STEP 2 OF 3","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.stepBadge3":"STEP 3 OF 3","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextBody1":'What this looks like depends on the template you chose. For document writing, you provide example documents and structure. For summaries, you define the audience, purpose, and focus. For expert answers, you add trusted source files. This helps the agent understand what to do and what "good" looks like.',"scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextBody2":"The result is more relevant, grounded responses—and a clear baseline of how your agent is performing against your goals.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextBoldLine":"Set your agent's goals and success metrics to measure and track the impact of tuning.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextSubtitle":"Ground the agent in your goals and examples","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextTab":"Tune Context","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneContextTitle":"Tune Context","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneModelBody1":"For advanced scenarios, you can tune the underlying model to improve reasoning quality and consistency.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneModelBody2":"Model tuning uses high-quality examples from your organisation to teach the agent how to respond in ways that better match your expectations—such as preferred tone, structure, decision-making patterns, or handling of edge cases. This goes beyond adding context or tools by refining how the agent interprets inputs and produces outputs. Model tuning is evaluated against the same goals you've defined, so you can see whether changes meaningfully improve agent performance.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneModelSubtitle":"Boost your agent's performance with high-quality example outputs","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneModelTab":"Tune Model","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneModelTitle":"Tune Model","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneToolsBody1":"You can add tools such as document validation or style editing to support the workflow you want the agent to follow.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneToolsBody2":"Connect your agent to other tuned agents to take on more complex tasks. Save this page to update your evaluation results.","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneToolsSubtitle":"Support the workflow you want the agent to follow","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneToolsTab":"Tune Tools","scc-react-copilot-tuning-preferences.copilotTuningTeachingMoment.tuneToolsTitle":"Tune Tools","scc-react-cot-panel.cotPanel.autoScrollButtonAriaLabel":"Follow activity","scc-react-cot-panel.cotPanel.dismissAriaLabel":"Close 